{"type":"text","timestamp":1775842989240,"sessionID":"ses_28782ed72ffegpf1AjZKbjAZFn","part":{"id":"prt_d787d929a001lEZe5CAjEJDvdr","messageID":"msg_d787d8872001u3714dJDM6251F","sessionID":"ses_28782ed72ffegpf1AjZKbjAZFn","type":"text","text":"Now I'll create the tasks.md checklist for AR-005 based on the design document and TDD manifest:","time":{"start":1775842989238,"end":1775842989238}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843055712,"sessionID":"ses_28782ed72ffegpf1AjZKbjAZFn","part":{"id":"prt_d787d94b7001zMLMu5FjtYAuVN","messageID":"msg_d787d8872001u3714dJDM6251F","sessionID":"ses_28782ed72ffegpf1AjZKbjAZFn","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_1b742eef996c4fb4bea2ed23","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/tasks.md","content":"# AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 Tasks\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-3 completed |\n\n## Atomic Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: Data Structures & Types\n\n- [ ] **TASK-001**: Define `CreateSandboxRequest` struct in `pkg/common/types.go`\n  - Fields: `Kind`, `Name`, `Namespace` (all string)\n  - Method: `Validate()` returning error\n  - Validation rules: Kind ∈ {AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter}, Namespace non-empty, Name non-empty\n\n- [ ] **TASK-002**: Define `CreateSandboxResponse` struct in `pkg/common/types.go`\n  - Fields: `SessionID`, `SandboxID`, `SandboxName` (string), `EntryPoints` ([]SandboxEntryPoint)\n\n- [ ] **TASK-003**: Define `SandboxEntryPoint` struct in `pkg/common/types.go`\n  - Fields: `Path`, `Protocol`, `Endpoint` (all string)\n\n- [ ] **TASK-004**: Define context keys in `pkg/workloadmanager/auth.go`\n  - Keys: `contextKeyUserToken`, `contextKeyServiceAccount`, `contextKeyServiceAccountName`, `contextKeyNamespace`\n\n- [ ] **TASK-005**: Define constants in `pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go`\n  - Constants: `DefaultSandboxTTL` (8h), `DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout` (15m), label/annotation keys\n\n### Phase 2: Infrastructure Components\n\n- [ ] **TASK-010**: Implement `sandboxCreator` struct in `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator.go`\n  - Fields: `k8sClient`, `sandboxController`, `storeClient`, `publicKey`\n\n- [ ] **TASK-011**: Implement `createSandbox()` method for `sandboxCreator`\n  - Steps: register watcher → store placeholder → create CR → wait (2min) → resolve IP → update store\n  - Rollback on failure: delete CR + delete store entry\n  - Use independent 30s timeout context for rollback delete\n\n- [ ] **TASK-012**: Implement `resolvePodIP()` method in `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder.go`\n  - Priority: sandbox name → annotation `agents.x-k8s.io/sandbox-pod-name` → informer cache → label selector\n  - Require PodRunning phase and non-empty PodIP\n\n- [ ] **TASK-013**: Implement `buildEntryPoints()` function in `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder.go`\n  - Input: podIP, []TargetPort\n  - Output: []SandboxEntryPoint with format `host:port`\n\n### Phase 3: Workload Builders\n\n- [ ] **TASK-020**: Implement `buildSandboxObject()` in `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder.go`\n  - Input: *AgentRuntime, sessionID\n  - Name format: `{workloadName}-{RandString(8)}`\n  - Set labels: session-id, workload-name, sandbox-name, managed-by\n  - Set annotations: idle-timeout\n  - Copy podTemplate from runtime.Spec.Template\n  - Set replicas=1, lifecycle.shutdownTime=now+MaxSessionDuration\n\n- [ ] **TASK-021**: Implement `buildSandboxClaimObject()` in `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder.go`\n  - For CodeInterpreter with WarmPoolSize > 0\n  - Minimal metadata, no full PodSpec\n  - APIVersion: `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`, Kind: `SandboxClaim`\n\n- [ ] **TASK-022**: Implement AuthMode injection for CodeInterpreter\n  - If AuthMode=picod and publicKey available: inject `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` env var\n  - Support optional fields: Command, Args, Environment, Resources, RuntimeClassName, ImagePullPolicy, ImagePullSecrets\n\n### Phase 4: HTTP Handlers\n\n- [ ] **TASK-030**: Implement `handleAgentRuntimeCreate()` in `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/agent_runtime.go`\n  - Parse JSON → set Kind=AgentRuntime → Validate()\n  - Get AgentRuntime from informer lister\n  - Check podTemplate non-nil\n  - Call createSandbox()\n  - Return CreateSandboxResponse (200) or error\n\n- [ ] **TASK-031**: Implement `handleCodeInterpreterCreate()` in `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/code_interpreter.go`\n  - Similar to AgentRuntime but:\n  - Kind=CodeInterpreter\n  - Support WarmPoolSize > 0 → buildSandboxClaimObject()\n  - Support AuthMode (picod/none)\n  - Default ports: [{Port: 8080, Protocol: \"HTTP\", PathPrefix: \"/\"}] if spec.Ports empty\n\n- [ ] **TASK-032**: Register routes in `pkg/workloadmanager/routes.go`\n  - POST /v1/agent-runtime → handleAgentRuntimeCreate\n  - DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId → handleDeleteSandbox\n  - POST /v1/code-interpreter → handleCodeInterpreterCreate\n  - DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId → handleDeleteSandbox\n\n- [ ] **TASK-033**: Implement `handleDeleteSandbox()` in `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/agent_runtime.go`\n  - Load session from store by sessionId\n  - NotFound → 404 with message `Session ID <id> not found, maybe already deleted`\n  - Delete SandboxClaim if Kind=SandboxClaim, else delete Sandbox\n  - API NotFound on delete → treat as success\n  - DeleteSandboxBySessionID from store\n  - Return 200 `{\"message\":\"Sandbox deleted successfully\"}`\n\n### Phase 5: Error Handling\n\n- [ ] **TASK-040**: Define error constants in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/validation.go` or `pkg/workloadmanager/response/response.go`\n  - ErrAgentRuntimeNotFound, ErrCodeInterpreterNotFound, ErrTemplateMissing, ErrPublicKeyMissing\n\n- [ ] **TASK-041**: Implement error mapping in handlers\n  - JSON bind失败 → 400 `Invalid request body`\n  - Validate 失败 → 400 `<field> is required`\n  - Template missing → 400 with `pod template` in message\n  - NotFound from informer → 404 `agent runtime not found` / `code interpreter not found`\n  - Auth失败 → 401 from authMiddleware\n  - Timeout/internal → 500 `internal server error`\n\n- [ ] **TASK-042**: Implement rollback strategy in `createSandbox()`\n  - CR 创建前失败: delete store placeholder\n  - CR 创建后超时: delete CR (30s timeout) + delete store\n  - Pod IP 解析失败: delete CR + delete store\n  - Store 更新失败: log warning, CR left for GC\n\n### Phase 6: Integration\n\n- [ ] **TASK-050**: Integrate with `client-go` typed clients\n  - Use `AgentRuntimeInterface` and `CodeInterpreterInterface` for reading templates\n  - Use informers + listers for cached reads\n\n- [ ] **TASK-051**: Integrate with dynamic client\n  - Create Sandbox/SandboxClaim CRs using `dynamic.Interface`\n  - GVR: `SandboxGVR`, `SandboxClaimGVR`\n\n- [ ] **TASK-052**: Integrate with SandboxReconciler\n  - Call `WatchSandboxOnce(ns, name)` before CR creation\n  - Wait on channel with 2min timeout\n  - Receive notification when status=running\n\n- [ ] **TASK-053**: Integrate with Store\n  - StoreSandbox() with placeholder before CR create\n  - UpdateSandbox() with full info after IP resolution\n  - DeleteSandboxBySessionID() on rollback or delete\n\n- [ ] **TASK-054**: Integrate with authMiddleware\n  - When EnableAuth=true: use per-user dynamic client from `GetOrCreateUserK8sClient`\n  - Cache key: `<namespace>:<serviceAccountName>`\n\n### Phase 7: Testing (TDD)\n\n#### Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **TEST-001**: `TestCreateSandboxRequest_Validate` in `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_test.go`\n  - Valid request → no error\n  - Empty name → error contains `name is required`\n  - Empty namespace → error contains `namespace is required`\n  - Invalid kind → error contains `kind is required`\n\n- [ ] **TEST-002**: `TestHandleAgentRuntimeCreate_Success` (TestCase-WM-001)\n  - Given: valid AgentRuntime in informer cache\n  - When: POST /v1/agent-runtime with valid JSON\n  - Then: 200, response contains sessionId and entryPoints\n  - Use fake clientset + mock store + mock SandboxReconciler\n\n- [ ] **TEST-003**: `TestHandleAgentRuntimeCreate_Idempotent` (TestCase-WM-002)\n  - Given: two consecutive requests with same name\n  - When: first creation succeeds\n  - Then: second returns same sessionId\n\n- [ ] **TEST-004**: `TestHandleAgentRuntimeCreate_MissingPodTemplate` (TestCase-WM-003)\n  - Given: AgentRuntime with spec.podTemplate=nil\n  - When: POST /v1/agent-runtime\n  - Then: 400, message contains `pod template`\n\n- [ ] **TEST-005**: `TestHandleCodeInterpreterCreate_WarmPool`\n  - Given: CodeInterpreter with WarmPoolSize > 0\n  - When: POST /v1/code-interpreter\n  - Then: creates SandboxClaim, response Kind=SandboxClaim\n\n- [ ] **TEST-006**: `TestHandleCodeInterpreterCreate_DefaultPorts`\n  - Given: CodeInterpreter with empty spec.Ports\n  - When: creation succeeds\n  - Then: entryPoints contains default 8080/HTTP\n\n- [ ] **TEST-007**: `TestHandleCodeInterpreterCreate_AuthModePicoD`\n  - Given: AuthMode=picod and publicKey available\n  - When: sandbox created\n  - Then: PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY env var injected\n\n- [ ] **TEST-008**: `TestHandleCodeInterpreterCreate_AuthModeNone`\n  - Given: AuthMode=none\n  - When: sandbox created\n  - Then: no PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY env var\n\n- [ ] **TEST-009**: `TestCreateSandbox_Timeout`\n  - Given: no running notification within 2min\n  - When: createSandbox() waits\n  - Then: error `sandbox creation timed out`, CR deleted, store entry deleted\n\n- [ ] **TEST-010**: `TestCreateSandbox_RollbackOnIPResolutionFailure`\n  - Given: pod IP resolution fails\n  - When: createSandbox() attempts to resolve\n  - Then: CR deleted, store entry deleted, error returned\n\n- [ ] **TEST-011**: `TestResolvePodIP_FromAnnotation`\n  - Given: Sandbox with annotation `agents.x-k8s.io/sandbox-pod-name`\n  - When: resolvePodIP() called\n  - Then: uses annotated pod name\n\n- [ ] **TEST-012**: `TestResolvePodIP_FromOwnerReference`\n  - Given: pods listed by label, one has owner reference Kind=Sandbox\n  - When: resolvePodIP() called\n  - Then: selects pod with matching owner reference\n\n- [ ] **TEST-013**: `TestResolvePodIP_PodNotRunning`\n  - Given: pod in Pending/Failed phase\n  - When: resolvePodIP() called\n  - Then: error indicating pod not running\n\n- [ ] **TEST-014**: `TestBuildSandboxObject_LabelsAndAnnotations`\n  - Given: AgentRuntime with sessionTimeout\n  - When: buildSandboxObject() called\n  - Then: labels and annotations set correctly\n\n- [ ] **TEST-015**: `TestBuildSandboxClaimObject_MinimalMetadata`\n  - Given: CodeInterpreter with WarmPoolSize > 0\n  - When: buildSandboxClaimObject() called\n  - Then: minimal metadata, no PodSpec\n\n- [ ] **TEST-016**: `TestHandleDeleteSandbox_Success`\n  - Given: session exists in store\n  - When: DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId\n  - Then: 200, CR deleted, store entry deleted\n\n- [ ] **TEST-017**: `TestHandleDeleteSandbox_NotFound` (Spec requirement)\n  - Given: no session key in store\n  - When: DELETE invoked\n  - Then: 404, message contains session id\n\n#### Test Infrastructure\n\n- [ ] **TEST-020**: Create `testEnv` struct in `pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go`\n  - Fields: k8sClient, reconciler, store, server, redis (miniredis), fakeClient, dynamicClient\n\n- [ ] **TEST-021**: Implement `newTestEnv(t *testing.T)` function\n  - Start miniredis\n  - Create fake clientset with registered AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter\n  - Create fake dynamic client\n  - Initialize K8sClient, SandboxReconciler, Store\n  - Build Server (auth/TLS disabled)\n\n- [ ] **TEST-022**: Create mock implementations\n  - MockWorkloadManager interface\n  - Mock SandboxReconciler.WatchSandboxOnce returning controllable channel\n\n#### Integration Tests\n\n- [ ] **TEST-030**: `TestE2E_CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox`\n  - Deploy AgentCube (Helm install to Kind cluster)\n  - Create ServiceAccount and get token\n  - POST /v1/agent-runtime\n  - Verify response contains sessionId and entryPoints\n  - Access sandbox via entryPoint to verify connectivity\n  - DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId to cleanup\n\n- [ ] **TEST-031**: E2E fixture `echo_agent.yaml`\n  - Simple echo server AgentRuntime definition\n\n#### Coverage Verification\n\n- [ ] **TEST-040**: Run coverage check\n  - Command: `go test -race -v -coverprofile=coverage.out -coverpkg=./pkg/... ./pkg/...`\n  - Verify test code / business code ratio > 0.4\n  - Verify each .go file has corresponding _test.go\n\n### Phase 8: Documentation\n\n- [ ] **DOC-001**: Add API examples to handler doc comments\n  - Example request/response for POST /v1/agent-runtime\n  - Example request/response for POST /v1/code-interpreter\n\n- [ ] **DOC-002**: Document error scenarios in handler doc comments\n  - List all HTTP status codes and conditions\n\n- [ ] **DOC-003**: Update pkg/workloadmanager/README.md\n  - Architecture diagram\n  - Component interaction flow\n  - Configuration options\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] All handlers implemented and registered\n- [ ] All tests pass (unit + integration)\n- [ ] Test coverage ratio > 0.4\n- [ ] Error handling covers all spec-defined scenarios\n- [ ] Rollback strategy verified by tests\n- [ ] Integration with client-go, informers, dynamic client, Store, SandboxReconciler complete\n- [ ] Auth mode (EnableAuth) tested with per-user client cache\n- [ ] WarmPool support for CodeInterpreter verified\n- [ ] Timeout (2min) and rollback (30s) enforced\n- [ ] Pod IP resolution covers all paths (annotation, owner reference, label selector)\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- **Completed**: ST-1 (CRD schemas), ST-2 (HTTP framework, auth middleware, informers)\n- **Required**: client-go typed clients, informers, listers operational\n- **Required**: SandboxReconciler operational (from controller package)\n- **Required**: Store interface (Redis-backed) operational\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775843055700,"end":1775843055709}}}}
